snippet.title: The Lost Chapter: Yuki’s Revenge | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Quentin Tarantino had a dream of a Kill Bill chapter that never made it to the silver screen, a chapter known as “Yuki’s Revenge.” Over 20 years later, Tarantino and Epic have come together to bring the story to life in Fortnite. 

Tarantino’s The Lost Chapter: Yuki’s Revenge stars Uma Thurman and premieres in Fortnite on November 30 at 2 PM ET! Doors open 30 minutes before the show starts. #fortnite #fortniteseven

snippet.title: KIS KISKO PYAAR KAROON 2: Official Trailer | Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh |In Cinemas 12 December 2025
snippet.description:
Kapil Sharma is back with his clean comedy capers and how 🎬🤣 
Presenting the official trailer of 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2', starring Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh, Hira Warina, Tridha Choudhary, Parul Gulati and others. This is a sequel to the blockbuster 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon', Kapil Sharma's debut film.  #KisKiskoPyaarKaroon2 #KapilSharma #ManjotSingh 

Experience this laugh riot with your entire family in cinemas on 12th December 2025 🤣🤣

'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2' is presented by Star Studio18 & Venus Worldwide Entertainment in association with Abbas Mustan Films Production, is written & directed by Anukalp Goswami and is produced by Ratan Jain, Ganesh Jain & Abbas Mustan.

The story will follow Harry’s son, Albus Potter, as he grapples with his family legacy and the weight of being the child of the "chosen one."

Fans are excited for magical duels, heartfelt moments, and a new generation of characters. The plot could explore the impact of the past on the present and the consequences of meddling with time. Expect heartwarming reunions, magical mishaps, and high-stakes adventure that brings the wizarding world back to life.

Nothing confirmed yet, but insiders suggest that Harry Potter and the Cursed Child will be an emotional and magical continuation of the saga that brings the beloved cast back for one more thrilling journey.

snippet.title: "MTG Has Broken Cover" - Marsh Family parody of "Billie Jean" by MJ about Marjorie Taylor Greene
snippet.description:
The song Billy Jean was a fictional narrative about a woman who makes false claims and goes from desirable to undesirable. Released in 1983, it was the second single from the fantastic album “Thriller” and became Jackson’s best selling solo single. Lots of his lyrics address paranoia and distrust, but it was the fit of the protagonist’s name in the chorus that really clinched an idea for us to take on this classic pop-disco track.

We’ve twisted the words around the story of Marjorie Taylor Greene, and how one of the vocal “Big Beasts” of Trump’s support base has now rancorously broken with him. You can find news about the topic here (from the wobbling coverage of the BBC): https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cwywjz202r7o.amp. 

We’re dedicating this song to Larry Jensen who generously supported our debut album release with the “parody parachute” reward on Kickstarter.

___________________________ 

If you want something more festive and less caustic, then PLEASE pre-order and check out our forthcoming Christmas single (out Friday 5th December) which is a cover of "Keeping the Dream Alive" by Münchener Freiheit and is raising funds and awareness for the Tiny Toes neonatal and special care baby units in our area - in support of an amazing local family. 

Pre-order here on whatever music platform: https://orcd.co/keepthedream

(And if you're going to stream it, fab, but please consider making a little donation to the Clark Family's JustGiving: https://justgiving.com/page/81colonelslanelights2025)

___________________________ 

Support us here: 
- PayPal to leave us a tip jar: https://paypal.me/marshfamilysongs 
- Patreon for ongoing support & bonuses: https://www.patreon.com/marshfamilysongs 
- Crowdfunder for debut album out in 2026: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/marshfamily/the-marsh-family-debut-album-campaign 

Find our other channels here: https://linktr.ee/marshfamilysongs 

Follow us here: 
- https://www.marshfamilysongs.com 
- https://www.facebook.com/MarshFamilySongs/ 
- https://www.instagram.com/marshfamilysongs/ 
- https://twitter.com/MarshSongs 
- https://www.threads.net/@marshfamilysongs 
- https://www.tiktok.com/@marshfamilysongs 
- https://bsky.app/profile/marshfamilysongs.bsky.social 
- https://open.spotify.com/artist/6AYmbCwi92V29y69lkRkRa 
___________________________ 

LYRICS:

She was sort of a MAGA queen - and she made a scene
Obsessed with finding conspiracies, liked her QAnon
Any stance, she could sure double down!
She defied everyone
Took her chance, getting more media rounds
Her parents had named her “Marjorie” - which was kind of mean
Maybe it led her to try to dream of ownin’ a gun
That’s her answer to all that goes wrong!

She wrote lots of stories ‘bout shootings in the schools
Went around spreading junk and hurt (hee-hee)
And then in 2016, she chased the moon for Trump
But be careful what you do (oh-oh)
‘Cause the tide could turn on you (oh-oh, hey-ey) [or keep original: ‘Cause the lie becomes the truth]

Taylor Greene has broken cover!
She’s just the first of many Republicans
Wish they did not vote for Trump
She said he was “the one”
But her confidence has gone

On Trump’s campaigns and on Party nights, she was by his side
She played her hand and had few demands
Her screams and rants
Brought him fans from bizarre stomping grounds
But it came at a price
Just a tool in a fool’s paradise!
(Do think twice) do think twice (ah-hoo)
She wasn’t happy with policy - and got crotchety
She goaded him about all his lyin’ - then just resigned (oh, no)
Took a stand, final straw, honour-bound (ooh, hee-hee-hee)

She’s no quiet piggy … she dared to have a feud
She went to town on his Epstein farce
He can say that she is wacky
Just a traitor he’ll deplume
It’s happened much too soon
Has he lost the locker room?!

MTG has broken cover!
She found the world insane inside Washington
But don’t kid yourself she’s done
No-no-no (hoo)
MTG’s now under cover
She’ll just return, repainted, firing her guns
So expect more hit and runs
Has the blowback begun?
Well, the mid-terms might be fun!

snippet.title: Interplanetary Criminal | Mixmag Lab London 2025
snippet.description:
Interplanetary Criminal is back in the Mixmag Lab London, this time as our latest cover star, shelling out 90 minutes of unrestrained UK Garage, Bassline and Speed Garage bangers. Does he have the most dangerous USB in the game? We'll let you decide.
The Mixmag Lab London is brought to you from No90 Hideout in Hackney Wick.
Like merch? Shop here: https://mixmag.shop/
Like this? Subscribe: https://bit.ly/subscribemixmag

Interplanetary Criminal is the Manchester-based producer, DJ and ATW Records co-founder leading a rip-roaring new wave of UK garage. Straight from the studio to the iconic Arcadia spider, and from Dekmantel to Depot Mayfield, Croatia, Bogotá, Sydney, Miami and all-nighters at Leeds' beloved Wire, IPC and his speedy, rowdy sets — and speedier, rowdier productions — are connecting with up-for-it audiences. His formula? Fresh, fun and foundation-minded, balancing innovation with a wholehearted appreciation for everything that's come before, including the enduring influence of the North West.

Set Sail for Glory - War Sails has arrived!

The seas of Calradia open today with the release of War Sails, the epic single-player expansion for Mount & Blade II: Bannerlord.

Sail the high seas, lead mighty fleets, and forge your legacy as you command powerful ships, engage in thrilling naval battles, and master maritime conquest. Embark on daring adventures across new territories with fresh mechanics, dangerous challenges, and a fully realized naval progression system. Customize your fleet, conquer coastal settlements, and carve your legend on the open waters.

Today, we're also releasing our v1.3.4 base game update which introduces many new mechanics like alliances & trade agreements, stealth & disguise, fast mode, and much more. You can read the full patch notes here - https://www.taleworlds.com/en/News/587
